I moved away from Saint Louis---to Europe---in 1994. I was not familiar with three of these TV series.
Since buying this "teaser-compilation", I bought the one-season run of "ACTION"; "NED & STACY:
Season 1"; and the three available seasons of "Just Shoot Me!"

Since you are more familiar with these programs than I am, I'll just say it's a great sampler, and I like
the '90s nostalgia! The video and audio was excellent.
